From e262b44399a4179f1902c506eec0523e31700b8b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Eyal Reizer <eyalr@ti.com>
Date: Tue, 11 Feb 2014 11:00:29 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 0774/1587] omap2plus_defconfig: expose tty emulation for hci

* Expose /dev/hci_tty driver emulation for hci.
  This allows easy integration of broad market bluetooth stacks
  over TI wilink chipset.
* Activate CONFIG_BT_WILINK needed by TI_ST

Signed-off-by: Eyal Reizer <eyalr@ti.com>
[zou: Original patch taken from
ti-sdk-am335x-evm-08.00.00.00-Linux-x86-Install.bin]
Signed-off-by: Cao Zou <cao.zou@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm/configs/omap2plus_defconfig |    3 +++
 1 files changed, 3 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/configs/omap2plus_defconfig b/arch/arm/configs/omap2plus_defconfig
index 0d61be0..c1805b0 100644
--- a/arch/arm/configs/omap2plus_defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm/configs/omap2plus_defconfig
@@ -72,6 +72,7 @@ CONFIG_BT_HCIUART_BCSP=y
 CONFIG_BT_HCIUART_LL=y
 CONFIG_BT_HCIBCM203X=m
 CONFIG_BT_HCIBPA10X=m
+CONFIG_BT_WILINK=m
 CONFIG_CFG80211=m
 CONFIG_MAC80211=m
 CONFIG_MAC80211_RC_PID=y
@@ -307,3 +308,5 @@ CONFIG_LIBCRC32C=y
 CONFIG_FONTS=y
 CONFIG_FONT_8x8=y
 CONFIG_FONT_8x16=y
+CONFIG_TI_ST=y
+CONFIG_ST_HCI=y
